So let me pick another color
here, that I haven't used.

00:11:02.010 --> 00:11:04.220
If you lend to the doctor,
once again, the risk

00:11:04.220 --> 00:11:06.110
is a little bit
higher than lending

00:11:06.110 --> 00:11:08.380
to that company or
the savings account.

00:11:08.380 --> 00:11:10.790
Once again, a little
bit higher reward.

00:11:10.790 --> 00:11:12.110
Little bit higher reward.

