Let me pick a color
I haven't used yet.

00:11:19.360 --> 00:11:21.570
Investing in the stock
market, Once again,

00:11:21.570 --> 00:11:23.470
higher risk, but
also a higher reward.

00:11:23.470 --> 00:11:25.490
Maybe 10 per year.

00:11:25.490 --> 00:11:26.880
That's 10% right over there.

00:11:26.880 --> 00:11:29.560
Your brother-in-law,
super high risk,

00:11:29.560 --> 00:11:31.100
probably off the
charts over here,

00:11:31.100 --> 00:11:32.630
but also super high reward.

00:11:32.630 --> 00:11:34.450
So maybe it might be like that.

00:11:34.450 --> 00:11:38.210
But the general idea is, the
more risk, the more reward.

